<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>Memberships</title>
     <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/MembershipPage.css">
</head>
<body>

     <!--Navigation Bar-->
     <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
          <div class="container-fluid">
               <!-- Logo -->
               <a class="navbar-brand" href="@Url.Action("index", "Home")">
                    <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/img/Logo.png")" alt="Gym Logo" class="brand-logo">
                    <span class="brand-text">MADGYM</span>
               </a>

               <!-- Sidebar Toggle Button (Only for Mobile) -->
               <button class="navbar-toggler d-lg-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasSidebar" aria-controls="offcanvasSidebar">
                    &#9776;

               </button>

               <!-- Standard Navbar Links (Hidden on Mobile) -->
               <div class="collapse navbar-collapse d-none d-lg-flex" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                         <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">About</a></li>
                         <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Services", "Home")">Services</a></li>
                         <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Membership", "Home")">Membership</a></li>
                         <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")">Contact</a></li>
                         <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Login", "Home")">Login</a></li>
                    </ul>
               </div>
          </div>
     </nav>

     <!-- Offcanvas Sidebar (For Mobile Navigation) -->
     <div class="offcanvas offcanvas-start" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasSidebar" aria-labelledby="offcanvasSidebarLabel">
          <div class="offcanvas-header">
               <h5 class="offcanvas-title" id="offcanvasSidebarLabel">Menu</h5>
               <button type="button" class="btn-close text-reset" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas" aria-label="Close"></button>
          </div>
          <div class="offcanvas-body">
               <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">About</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Services", "Home")">Services</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Membership", "Home")">Membership</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")">Contact</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("Login", "Home")">Login</a></li>
               </ul>
          </div>
     </div>
     <!-- Header Section -->
     <header class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-5" style="margin-top: 60px;">
          <h1>Choose the Perfect Membership for You</h1>
          <p>Discover the benefits of each plan and start today!</p>
     </header>

     <!-- Cards Section -->
     <section id="plans" class="container my-1">
          <div class="row">
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-secondary text-white">Basic</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Limited access to features.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">$10/month</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">Standard</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Access to all equipment.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">1 guided training session/month.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">$40/month</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">Premium</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">VIP access.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Personal trainer.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">$60/month</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">Elite</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Personal trainer and priority access.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">$100/month</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-warning text-white">Friends</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Access for 3 members.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">$120/month</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-md-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="card text-center d-flex flex-column h-100" style="min-height: 320px;">
                         <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white">Corporate</div>
                         <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Access for employees.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Mon-Fri: 3:00 PM - 10:00 PM.</p>
                              <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">Sat-Sun: 8:00 AM - 3:00 PM.</p>
                              <h5 class="card-title text-danger">Negotiable price</h5>
                              <a href="#plans" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" style="width: 100px; margin: 0 auto; display: block;">Choose</a>
                         </div>
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>
     </section>

     <section class="container my-5 text-white">
          <div class="row">
               <div class="col-12">
                    <h2>Membership Benefits</h2>
                    <p>Each membership offers a set of benefits to help you achieve your fitness goals. No matter which plan you choose, you'll enjoy a motivating environment and top-notch equipment to enhance your gym experience.</p>
                    <p>Our memberships are flexible and cater to the needs of all types of users, from beginners to experienced athletes.</p>
                    <p>We look forward to seeing you!</p>
               </div>
          </div>
     </section>

     <script src="~/Scripts/MembershipPage.js"></script>
     <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
